OL,3,CMinisters warned rental reforms will
OL,4,Climit access to higher education
OL,6,FFlagship reforms of the private rented
OL,7,Fsector will limit access to higher
OL,8,Feducation and stifle social mobility,
OL,9,Flandlords and student housing
OL,10,Fproviders claim.
OL,12,FAhead of the second reading of the
OL,13,FRenters' Rights Bill in the House of
OL,14,FLords on Tuesday, the Government has
OL,15,Fbeen warned that a move to end fixed
OL,16,Fterm tenancy agreements will threaten
OL,17,Fthe annual cycle of the student
OL,18,Fhousing market.
