OL,3,CMinisters warned rental reforms will
OL,4,Climit access to higher education
OL,6,FA coalition including housing
OL,7,Fproviders and property portals said
OL,8,Fthe legislation in its current form
OL,9,Fwill lead to one and two-bedroom
OL,10,Fstudent homes falling outside measures
OL,11,Fto protect the yearly cycle of the
OL,12,Frest of the market.
OL,14,FAnalysis of data held by the
OL,15,Forganisations shows there will be no
OL,16,Fguarantee that at least a fifth of all
OL,17,Fexisting student housing in England
OL,18,Fwill be available to rent at the start
OL,19,Fof each academic year, they said.
