OL,3,CMinisters warned rental reforms will
OL,4,Climit access to higher education
OL,6,FIn a letter to skills minister
OL,7,FBaroness Smith, the organisations
OL,8,Fwarned that without changes to the
OL,9,FBill, many students will not be able
OL,10,Fto access the housing they need and,
OL,11,Fas a consequence, their higher
OL,12,Feducation options will be limited.
OL,14,FIn addition, the Government's plan to
OL,15,Frestrict the payment of rent in
OL,16,Fadvance will make it "near impossible"
OL,17,Ffor international students without a
OL,18,FUK credit history to prove their
OL,19,Fability to sustain a tenancy and pay
OL,20,Ftheir rents, the organisations said.
