OL,3,CMinisters warned rental reforms will
OL,4,Climit access to higher education
OL,6,F"The changes will ultimately prove to
OL,7,Fbe counterproductive, increasing
OL,8,Funcertainty and financial anxiety
OL,9,Famong student tenants. All it will
OL,10,Flead to is chaos and confusion for
OL,11,Fstudents, making it harder for them to
OL,12,Fsecure housing and ultimately
OL,13,Frestricting options for higher
OL,14,Feducation.
OL,16,F"We call on the Government and peers
OL,17,Fto act to protect the availability of
OL,18,Fall student housing."
